@database InfoTextClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - InfoText Class"


InfoText class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "TextClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The InfoText class is used to show an information text.

  InfoText is a subclass of InfoText.mcc so you must have
  InfoText.mcc in MUI:Libs/MUI to use it. InfoText.mcc is
  copyright of Benny Kjær Nielsen.

  Note that any attribute of Text class, e.g. Preparse may be
  used with InfoText.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Contents@{fg text}
  S SGN
  The actual contents of the InfoText. Note that after
  ExpirationPeriod, it expires and InfoText shows FallBackText or
  an empty string.

  @{fg shine}ExpirationPeriod@{fg text}
  N ISGN
  Milliseconds after which Contents expires, default 4000.

  @{fg shine}FallBackText@{fg text}
  S ISGN
  Text to show after expiration.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Timeout@{fg text}
  -
  Force expiration of Contents.

@EndNode
